race.comment: FABULANTES (2) was there on the corner but weakened out of contention in the Listed Gold Edition last time out. Given a five-week reset and won't find this as tough so he is in the right race to bounce back to form. FINANCIALLY FAMOUS (6) stalked the pace then went home a little too well in a Class 1 over 1110m at Doomben last weekend. Far tougher ask this time around but she is obviously going well so stick with her. READY FOR AIMEE (10) continues to race well deep into her maiden prep. Caught the eye when beaten under a length over this trip at Doomben last time. Each-way hope on the limit from a favourable draw. THE BEAR (1) tired at the end of 1300m here last time but is far better placed back to this trip.
